reviewText: We originally had the first two Stuart Little DVDs, but got this for my grandson's recent birthday. I hadn't seen the third, animated, video.He loves Stuart so much we watch at least one of these several times a week. He is always talking about Stuart.The rest of us enjoy watching Hugh Laurie in a totally different character than House. All of the characters were well chosen, and the Stuart Little movies are great family entertainment.I like that a lot of these movies slip in references that adults can enjoy. As many times as I have now seen all three, I still have fun!
summary: We Watch These Videos Almost Daily
Title: Stuart Little Movie Collection

reviewText: This is a movie set great for both young and old.  The animation mixed with live action was done flawlessly.
